title: The New Skins for Nidalee and Gnar
body: These new skins are good and all but they need to be fix when i play nidalee my spears are going though enemies and my mate was play Super Galaxy Gnar and his Q is doing the same thing please fix and let me know Thank You Riot :)

replies.body: I feel ya- bugs are super frustrating to play with. The best place to post this is the [Report a Bug](http://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/bug-report) sub-board on the North American Boards. Developers check that sub-board and will be able to better document bugs if they're posted there!
